From https://github.com/pytorch/torchtune

1. Easy-to-use fine-tuning native PyTorch library for creating, fine-tuning, and experimenting with LLMs.
2. Native PyTorch implementation of popular LLMs
3. Support for various checkpoint formats including HF format checkpoints
4. Providing training recipes for widely-used fine-tuning techniques through reference benchmarks and comprehensive accuracy checks
5. Model evaluation using the EleutherAI evaluation harness
6. Integration with HuggingFace datasets for training
7. Support for distributed training using PyTorch Distributed's FSDP
8. YAML configuration for easy setup of training runs

"""
[Scheduled] Support for low-precision dtype and quantization techniques with TorchAO
[Scheduled] Support for integration with various inference engines.
